WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:05.000
Barclays Online Banking

2
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.320
How to log in using your app ID

3
00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:13.200
Logging in to Online Banking using
your Barclays app ID is quick and easy.

4
00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:17.080
Start by entering your last name
and membership number as normal.

5
00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:23.200
After entering your details, you'll be given the
option to log in to Online Banking using the Barclays app.

6
00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:25.440
Click 'Send notification'.

7
00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:28.840
You'll now need to go to the app
the device is downloaded on.

8
00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:31.880
On the device, tap the message.

9
00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:36.400
Confirm it's you logging in to
Online Banking by tapping 'Confirm'

10
00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:39.440
and you should now be logged in to Online Banking.

11
00:00:39.560 --> 00:00:42.280
But when you return, if you see this screen,

12
00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:46.040
just click 'I've confirmed this' and you're good to go.

